		<title>寵物進入中老年期？這5大症狀與健康問題不可輕忽</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/01/%e5%af%b5%e7%89%a9%e9%80%b2%e5%85%a5%e4%b8%ad%e8%80%81%e5%b9%b4%e6%9c%9f%ef%bc%9f%e9%80%995%e5%a4%a7%e7%97%87%e7%8b%80%e8%88%87%e5%81%a5%e5%ba%b7%e5%95%8f%e9%a1%8c%e4%b8%8d%e5%8f%af%e8%bc%95%e5%bf%bd/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 01 Nov 2025 06:17:38 +0000</pubDate>
