		<title>狗狗總是愛「偷看」主人洗澡？這5種原因讓牠難以離開！</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/31/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e7%b8%bd%e6%98%af%e6%84%9b%e3%80%8c%e5%81%b7%e7%9c%8b%e3%80%8d%e4%b8%bb%e4%ba%ba%e6%b4%97%e6%be%a1%ef%bc%9f%e9%80%995%e7%a8%ae%e5%8e%9f%e5%9b%a0%e8%ae%93%e7%89%a0%e9%9b%a3%e4%bb%a5/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
